  "prompt": "Where can I get very traditional plastering service in Boston?",
  "response": "For traditional plastering services in Boston, you might want to consider reaching out to local businesses that specialize in historic restoration and traditional plaster work. Some options include:\n\n1. **Master Plastering & Services, Inc.** - Known for their expertise in traditional plastering techniques, including ornamental and restoration work.\n\n2. **Revere Plastering & Painting** - They offer a range of plastering services and have experience with older homes and traditional methods.\n\n3. **Baldwin & Sons Plastering** - A well-regarded local company with experience in traditional and ornamental plastering.\n\n4. **Historic Plaster Conservation Services** - While they focus on conservation, they also provide traditional plastering techniques that may be suitable for historic properties.\n\nYou can also check online directories, customer reviews on websites like Yelp or Angie's List, or ask for recommendations from local historical societies or preservation organizations, as they often work with specialists in traditional techniques.",
